"{\n  \"text\": \"Well, I'm very excited to announce I'm going to be leading a discussion at the Houston Health Museum on the microbiome and fermented foods on July 27th at between 5 and 7 p.m. That's a Thursday, and it's going to be called Cocktails and Conversations, or I should say it's part of their cocktails and conversations series. And so we'll be serving uh two cocktails per person. Uh, we're gonna cap it at about 30 people, so it's gonna be a very small and limited event. Uh you can get tickets at the Houston Health Museum events page, and it's gonna be just kind of an open discussion about all the things I talk about fermented foods, gut health, uh, microbes, uh, on and on on. I'm really looking forward to it. And like I say, it's not going to be just me talking, it's gonna be an open discussion about these things, so it's gonna be a lot of fun. Anyway, the Houston Health Museum events page, July 27th, 5 to 7 p.m. Uh Tales and Conversations. Thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Well, I'm very excited to announce I'm going to be leading a discussion at the Houston Health Museum on the microbiome and fermented foods on July 27th at between 5 and 7 p.m.\",\n      \"start\": 0.96,\n      \"end\": 15.28,\n      \"duration\": 14.32,\n      \"confidence\": 0.994,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" W\",\n          \"start\": 0.96,\n          \"end\": 1.28,\n          \"duration\": 0.32,\n          \"confidence\": 0.996\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ell\",\n          \"start\": 1.28,\n          \"end\": 1.28,\n          \"duration\": 0.0,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \",\",\n          \"start\": 1.28,\n          \"end\": 1.36,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 0.954\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" I\",\n          \"start\": 1.36,\n          \"end\": 1.52,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n